[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    100[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe problem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m EventBridge invokes Lambda asynchronously by default. Asynchronous Lambda invocations retry twice on failure (3 total attempts) before sending to a DLQ (if configured). Without a DLQ configured, failed invocations are silently dropped after retries.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    101[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
