[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    144[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe problem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The recipe says "VPC endpoints for Bedrock" without specifying the endpoint type. Bedrock uses interface endpoints (PrivateLink), not gateway endpoints. Interface endpoints require security group configuration (allow HTTPS inbound from Lambda subnet) and incur hourly per-AZ costs. A reader unfamiliar with the distinction may not configure the security group correctly.[K
