[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    136[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m##[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mGeneral Architecture Pattern[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    137[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    138[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mAt a conceptual level, a medication dispensing anomaly pipeline has to serve two very different latency regimes simultaneously. Some detection has to fire in near real time at order verification or dispense cabinet pull (because interrupting the wrong dose before it's drawn into a syringe is the whole point). Other detection runs on accumulated history for pattern and trend work. The architecture is a hybrid of streaming and batch, with a shared feature and reference-data layer underneath.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    139[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    140[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206m```[K
